snippet.title: Freshly Picked - Tingle's Rosy Rupeeland English Trailer
snippet.description:
Sorry bout' the borked aspect ratio :(

An English triler for Freshly Picked - Tingle's Rosy Rupeeland (aka Tingle RPG) found on Nintendo of Europes webiste.

This games comes out in Europe on September 14th, came out in Japan in 2006 and there is no word on a North American release.
